'''汉勒效应'''（{{lang-en|Hanle effect}}）指的是用偏振光激发原子，并在原子的特定方向加磁场时，原子发射光的偏振度减少的现象。这是[[德國|德國]]實驗物理學家[[威廉·汉勒|威廉·汉勒]]在1924年发现的，故以他的名字命名。<ref name="Abraham 2003">{{cite journal |author = J Alnis, K Blushs, M Auzinsh, S Kennedy, N Shafer-Ray, E R I Abraham |year = 2003 |title = The Hanle effect and level crossing spectroscopy in Rb vapour under strong laser excitation |journal = [[Journal_of_Physics_B|Journal of Physics B]] |volume = 36 |pages = 1161–1173 |doi = 10.1088/0953-4075/36/6/307 |url = http://www.nhn.ou.edu/~abe/research/OUReprints/The%20Hanle%20effect%20in%20Rb%20vapour%20under%20strong%20laser%20excitation.pdf |bibcode = 2003JPhB...36.1161A |access-date = 2013-12-23 |archive-date = 2016-03-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303185402/http://www.nhn.ou.edu/~abe/research/OUReprints/The%20Hanle%20effect%20in%20Rb%20vapour%20under%20strong%20laser%20excitation.pdf |dead-url = yes }}</ref>

==應用==
*观测太阳发射光的汉勒效应，可以间接测量太阳内部的磁场。

